Description
-----------

This is a very simple package that enables you to make a beep sound in python.

Requirements
------------

-  Python 3
-  sox

Install
-------

Using pip:
~~~~~~~~~~

::

    pip3 install --upgrade pybeep



Usage
-----

::

    from pybeep.pybeep import PyVibrate, PyBeep
    PyVibrate().beep()
    PyVibrate().beepn(3)
    PyBeep().beep()
    PyBeep().beepn(3)
